    <item>
      <title>加拿大央行将在关税酝酿之际缩减降息规模：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bank-of-canada-to-downsize-cuts-as-tariffs-brew-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行很可能在周三将利率下调四分之一个百分点，因为央行官员们正在分析美国关税将如何破坏加拿大经济的软着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bank-of-canada-to-downsize-cuts-as-tariffs-brew-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:59:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政府因美国停止拨款遭非营利组织起诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/trump-admin-sued-by-nonprofits-over-us-grant-halt-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普政府因一项暂停支付大量联邦补助贷款和援助的新计划而面临诉讼，此举可能影响美国数十亿美元的资金流动。彭博新闻社的杰克·菲茨帕特里克在“彭博：市场”节目中详细介绍了该诉讼的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-28/trump-admin-sued-by-nonprofits-over-us-grant-halt-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:37:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桥水基金的 Karniol-Tambour 表示增长前景利好股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bridgewater-s-karniol-tambour-says-growth-outlook-favors-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[桥水基金联席首席投资官凯伦·卡尼奥尔-坦布尔 (Karen Karniol-Tambour) 表示，由于经济复苏可能导致通胀维持高位，她更青睐股票而非债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bridgewater-s-karniol-tambour-says-growth-outlook-favors-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 18:07:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
