    <item>
      <title>橡树资本的霍华德·马克斯表示低利率时代不会很快回归</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oaktree-s-howard-marks-says-don-t-expect-low-rate-era-to-return</link>
      <description><![CDATA[橡树资本集团有限责任公司 (Oaktree Capital Group LLC) 联合创始人霍华德·马克斯 (Howard Marks) 表示，在轻松赚钱时代赚得盆满钵满的投资者不应期望同样的策略能够在未来带来如此丰厚的回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oaktree-s-howard-marks-says-don-t-expect-low-rate-era-to-return</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 16:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能行业动荡导致比特币下跌，为加密货币涨势蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bitcoin-btc-drop-fueled-by-deepseek-ai-shakeup-spurs-doubts-over-crypto-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 引发的全球市场动荡导致了数字资产的波动，继去年价格暴涨之后，人们对加密货币的前景产生了新的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/bitcoin-btc-drop-fueled-by-deepseek-ai-shakeup-spurs-doubts-over-crypto-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 02:36:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
